XML::SAX::Builder
=================

This is yet another module to attempt to make generation of XML
documents easier than the corresponding print statements...  In
particular, this implementation attempts to play nicely with SAX
pipelines and handle namespaces correctly.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Test::More (any version )
  XML::NamespaceSupport (any version)
  XML::SAX::Writer (any version)

